description.en:
National Geographic bird food DIY

Do you like arts and crafts and animals? Then this DIY bird food set is for you! Use seeds to make your own bird food. The birds are guaranteed to like it!

Gender: junior
Dimensions: 22 x 10 x 8 cm (lxwxh)
Age: 4 to 12 years

1 Set of peanuts
1 Bag of nuts
1 Bag of seed
1 Rope
